  "excerpt": "Is there a way to move an item directly to a selected group but positioned in the top instead of the default bottom?",
  "solvedPostId": null,
  "likeCount": 1,
  "views": 23,
  "posts": [
    {
      "id": 234158,
      "postNumber": 1,
      "createdAt": "2025-07-11T11:40:03.963Z",
      "author": "RenanBarros (Renan)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Is there a way to move an item directly to a selected group but positioned in the top instead of the default bottom?</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 234172,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2025-07-11T11:44:18.204Z",
      "author": "Clover_Gal (Desiree McCarthy | monday.com Ambassador)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>You could add a date column called ‘moved to this group’ (or something like that). Then set an automation that sets that date when the item is moved to the group. Then you’ll save sort by ‘date moved to group’.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/d/fd89f6abc9886c971f31da8ba1a4e248d15ca02e.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/f/d/fd89f6abc9886c971f31da8ba1a4e248d15ca02e_2_690x263.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"263\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1152×440 13.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Desiree - <a href=\"http://www.thecleverclovers.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">www.thecleverclovers.com</a></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 234218,
      "postNumber": 3,
      "createdAt": "2025-07-11T12:50:51.144Z",
      "author": "RenanBarros (Renan)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>That’s an interesting workaround. Thanks!</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 235530,
      "postNumber": 4,
      "createdAt": "2025-07-28T13:00:44.730Z",
      "author": "RenanBarros (Renan)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Can sorting work only on one group? Because we only needed it sorted like that in the one of our groups</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 235587,
      "postNumber": 5,
      "createdAt": "2025-07-28T13:14:45.365Z",
      "author": "Clover_Gal (Desiree McCarthy | monday.com Ambassador)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Sorting affects the whole view. What about then creating a view for that group where it’s sorted? Create a new ‘table’ view, then filter so it only shows that group and save the setting.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/e/0e977e3fd4e11c0024662cd3072609ef2932c539.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/e/0e977e3fd4e11c0024662cd3072609ef2932c539.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"428\" height=\"174\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">428×174 9.62 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/4/f4c9845c558ad480a2dd741bf0e58bf00bee40d6.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/f/4/f4c9845c558ad480a2dd741bf0e58bf00bee40d6_2_690x225.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"225\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1065×348 27.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Desiree - <a href=\"http://www.thecleverclovers.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">www.thecleverclovers.com</a></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 243843,
      "postNumber": 6,
      "createdAt": "2026-01-08T02:54:27.634Z",
      "author": "reinier (Reinier ― 📅 Calendar Plus 🍅 Automato)",
